# Typography (Raboteriya)

Use these typography styles consistently across sections.

## Section headings (e.g. About, feature blocks)

- **Font weight:** `font-black` (900)
- **Size:** `text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl`
- **Line height:** `leading-tight`
- **Color:** `text-gray-900` when on light background

Example:
```html
<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black leading-tight text-gray-900">...</h2>
```

## Base text (paragraphs, body copy)

- **Size:** `text-lg`
- **Color:** `text-gray-900`
- Use for all body paragraphs and readable content in sections.

Example:
```html
<p class="text-lg text-gray-900">...</p>
<!-- or wrapper: -->
<div class="text-lg text-gray-900 space-y-4">...</div>
```

Reference: `src/_includes/sections/home-about.njk` (heading + paragraphs).
